snippet.title: EMIWAY - THANKS TO GOD (Prod. by Pendo46) (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Lyrics given below

Artist & Lyrics - Emiway Bantai 

Music - Pendo46
https://www.youtube.com/user/Rillataan

Mix/Master - Emiway

Visuals by - Happy

Edited by -  Happy and Emiway

Production - Bantai studio 

Producer- Emiway Bantai

Emiway Management MAIL ID 
imailemiway@gmail.com

Social connect
Instagram - Emiway_Bantai
Facebook - Emiway37
Twitter - emiwaytweets

(Lyrics)
Ab mei accha karra tha
Abba ka kam hora tha thap par woh nai har manenge
Woh badalke rhenge kismat
Filal jo waqt tha woh kaagi saqt tha paisa usane se pehle deraha hu sadqah.Mujhe rehna hai strong Dhyan rakhna hai sabka pata bhi nai chala achanak se kaise tapka pareshani,chod gaya nishani yeah.Aj gana nai sunane aya hu kahani mei.

Subha ka waqt tha
Abba ke sar mei dard tha
Raat ko sone se pehle unke dil mei dar tha
Mummy ka call aya subhe boli woh jaldi se ghar aa
Mei bhagke jake dekha
Abba ka halat bigadta ja rha tha
andhar ka dard aj chehre pe dikha
Raha tha
Kha par leke jau kuch nhi smjh aa rha tha
Aese tese karke le gaya unko aspatal
Ek nai do nai teen nai char
Dekha nai tha unka aisa haal
Leke gaya unhe ambulance mei
Baithke
Pehchan nai rhe the abba
Mujhe dekhke
Mei dekhta hi rehgaya
Kafi din se roya nai tha lekin usdin behgaya
Malik pe tab bhi bharosa tha mei unse kehgaya
Man hi man mei
Mere abba ko lota do
Unke sapne ko pura karne ko firse ek mauka do
Theekh kaise karu mei unhe
rasta koi
Batado
Abba ko bachalo

Aisa lagra tha
Abba yad dash kho diye
Icu mei dekheke unhe ammi
Bhi roo diye
Par har nahi mane hum
Pata tha woh
Lotenge
Bure khayalat are the
Lekin hum
Rokenge
Chokenge jab dekhenge
Bhagwan ka karishma
Mei tut rha tha
Mujhe lagne laga sadma
Par anu ballu bhai Sumit minta
Shabana didi sab sath the
Family walo ne dia sath
Bole khuda sath hai

Sath hai khuda mere sath hai
Zindagi hai hi aisi cheez din
Kabhi raat hai (x3)
Sath hai sath hai khuda sabke
sath hai zindagi hai aisi cheez
Din kabhi raat hai kya

Alhumdulillah
All praises to allah
Almighty god is great
He is the greatest

Sabke bech rehke bhi akela pan sa mehsoos tha
Stress badnelaga tha
Mei thoda sa confuse tha
Par khoya nahi meine khudko
Shayat soch mei dalneki
Koshish mei hai
Rukko
Jao jhukko
Aur matha teko
Khudake saamne
Madad karenge teri woh khud aake samne
Aameen
Par jo hua hai usse meine kafi kuch seekha hai
Khush rehna seekhle
Khudse kyu roota hai
andhar se toota
Uthna majboot hoga
Zindagi mei
Aisa kabhi nai bolna ke zindagi hai meri
Gandagi mei
Jo bhi hota hai sab ke peeche kuch na kuch wajah
Dukhi tha mei 3 din
Lekin aj firse maza
aane laga hai
Abba pure theekh hogaye
Teri raza hai
Takleefo se ladke aur aage
Chala gaya mei
Kal toota tha lekin
Aj bilkul naya mei
Mei laut aya hu tere pass
Kaha tha chala gaya mei

#thankstogod #emiwaybantai #universe

snippet.title: SAOCOM 1B Mission
snippet.description:
SpaceX is targeting Sunday, August 30 at 7:18 p.m. EDT, or 23:18 UTC, for Falcon 9‚Äôs launch of the SAOCOM 1B mission, which will carry the SAOCOM 1B spacecraft to orbit in addition to two rideshare payloads, Tyvak-0172 and PlanetiQ‚Äôs GNOMES-1. The mission will lift off from Space Launch Complex 40 (SLC-40) at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station in Florida. A backup launch opportunity is available on Monday, August 31 at 7:19 p.m. EDT, or 23:19 UTC. This mission marks SpaceX‚Äôs first launch to a polar orbit from the East Coast, and the first polar launch from Florida in decades.

Falcon 9‚Äôs first stage previously launched Dragon to the International Space Station for SpaceX‚Äôs 19th and 20th commercial resupply missions, and it also supported launch of SpaceX‚Äôs ninth Starlink mission. Following stage separation, SpaceX will land Falcon 9 on Landing Zone 1 at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station. SAOCOM 1B will deploy approximately 14 minutes after launch, GNOMES-1 and Tyvak-0172 will deploy approximately 61 and 62 minutes after liftoff.

snippet.title: Surviving the Hottest Place in the World
snippet.description:
Go to http://www.audible.com/yestheory or text yestheory to 500 500 to get one free audiobook, unlimited Audible originals and a 30-day free trial
New Seek Discomfort Summer Drop: https://www.seekdiscomfort.com/ live for only 72hrs!

This week after Death Valley hit the hottest temperature ever recorded... We decided to go and experience what 130F or 56C felt like... Both the best and worst idea we've ever had.

Does anyone read the description? I never really know to be honest. Well either way, this is Thomas and I'm a bit bored writing this so I'll just keep typing random things and see if anybody will notice. Conor was really upset that we kept him farting in the video so please ignore that part (or don't). Anyways, hope you liked the video we're actually pretty stoked with how it came out!

Check out Conor's channel here and tell him we sent you it'll make him very happy!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1E5Ti2P70zZxA4osS2MhiA

Thank you to Tommy, Tristan and Nathan for tagging along as our rescue team.

We have a 2nd channel! Make sure to subscribe to it here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTd7KzdwnFE3lm6LCfYDmUQ

If you want to join the Yes Fam Facebook group which is 100,000+ of our most engaged and badass community members, you can apply here: 
https://www.facebook.com/groups/yesfam/

PERFECT ROYALTY FREE MUSIC FOR YOUTUBE: free 30 day trial here: http://share.epidemicsound.com/wFFbr 

Musicbed has amazing montage and cinematic music:
http://share.mscbd.fm/YesTheory

For an amazing b-roll and footage library, checkout: http://storyblocks.com/YesTheory

Yes Theory Spotify Playlist: 
https://open.spotify.com/user/t-boogy...

Exclusive challenges on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/yestheory/

Who are we? 
We believe that life can be as fulfilling as you wish, so long as you're willing to seek discomfort. And we make videos about it.

Business Inquiries: zack@yestheory.com
For community inquiries: hello@yestheory.com

https://www.instagram.com/yestheory/
https://twitter.com/yestheory
https://www.facebook.com/yestheory/
Join our texting community: +1 (323) 310-5420

Hosts: Thomas Brag, Ammar Kandil, Matt Dajer
Editors: Thomas Brag, Thomas Dajer, Cam Peddle, Bryce Perry
Produced by Lauren Rosen

snippet.title: Jon Rahm‚Äôs 66-foot birdie putt to win playoff at BMW Championship
snippet.description:
In the final round of the 2020 BMW Championship, Jon Rahm sinks a 66-foot birdie putt on the par-4 18th hole, the first in a sudden-death playoff with Dustin Johnson. DJ and Rahm are Nos. 1 and 2 in the Official World Golf Rankings and remain that way after this tournament. 

SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh

The PGA TOUR heads to Olympia Fields Country Club for the BMW Championship, which marks the final opportunity to earn a spot in the 30-man FedExCup Playoffs finale at East Lake. snippet.title: CLIPPERS at MAVERICKS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | August 30, 2020
snippet.description:
CLIPPERS at MAVERICKS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | August 30, 2020

Led by Kawhi Leonard‚Äôs 33 PTS, 14 REB, 7 AST and 5 STL, the LA Clippers defeated the Dallas Mavericks, 111-97, in Game 6. Leonard is the first player to have 25+ PTS, 10+ REB, and 5+ STL in a playoff game since Paul George on 4/28/14. Paul George added 15 PTS, 9 REB and 7 AST for the Clippers in the victory, while Luka Doncic paced the Mavericks with 38 PTS, 9 REB and 9 AST. The Clippers will now advance to the Western Conference Semifinals.

snippet.title: SAOCOM 1B Mission
snippet.description:
SpaceX is targeting Sunday, August 30 at 7:18 p.m. EDT, or 23:18 UTC, for Falcon 9‚Äôs launch of the SAOCOM 1B mission, which will carry the SAOCOM 1B spacecraft to orbit in addition to two rideshare payloads, Tyvak-0172 and PlanetiQ‚Äôs GNOMES-1. The mission will lift off from Space Launch Complex 40 (SLC-40) at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station in Florida. A backup launch opportunity is available on Monday, August 31 at 7:19 p.m. EDT, or 23:19 UTC. This mission marks SpaceX‚Äôs first launch to a polar orbit from the East Coast, and the first polar launch from Florida in decades.

Falcon 9‚Äôs first stage previously launched Dragon to the International Space Station for SpaceX‚Äôs 19th and 20th commercial resupply missions, and it also supported launch of SpaceX‚Äôs ninth Starlink mission. Following stage separation, SpaceX will land Falcon 9 on Landing Zone 1 at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station. SAOCOM 1B will deploy approximately 14 minutes after launch, GNOMES-1 and Tyvak-0172 will deploy approximately 61 and 62 minutes after liftoff.

snippet.title: Surviving the Hottest Place in the World
snippet.description:
Go to http://www.audible.com/yestheory or text yestheory to 500 500 to get one free audiobook, unlimited Audible originals and a 30-day free trial
New Seek Discomfort Summer Drop: https://www.seekdiscomfort.com/ live for only 72hrs!

This week after Death Valley hit the hottest temperature ever recorded... We decided to go and experience what 130F or 56C felt like... Both the best and worst idea we've ever had.

Does anyone read the description? I never really know to be honest. Well either way, this is Thomas and I'm a bit bored writing this so I'll just keep typing random things and see if anybody will notice. Conor was really upset that we kept him farting in the video so please ignore that part (or don't). Anyways, hope you liked the video we're actually pretty stoked with how it came out!

Check out Conor's channel here and tell him we sent you it'll make him very happy!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1E5Ti2P70zZxA4osS2MhiA

Thank you to Tommy, Tristan and Nathan for tagging along as our rescue team.

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTd7KzdwnFE3lm6LCfYDmUQ

snippet.title: Jon Rahm‚Äôs 66-foot birdie putt to win playoff at BMW Championship
snippet.description:
In the final round of the 2020 BMW Championship, Jon Rahm sinks a 66-foot birdie putt on the par-4 18th hole, the first in a sudden-death playoff with Dustin Johnson. DJ and Rahm are Nos. 1 and 2 in the Official World Golf Rankings and remain that way after this tournament. 

SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh

The PGA TOUR heads to Olympia Fields Country Club for the BMW Championship, which marks the final opportunity to earn a spot in the 30-man FedExCup Playoffs finale at East Lake. The field will feature the top 70 in the FedExCup standings, including two-time FedExCup champions Tiger Woods and Rory McIlroy, plus defending BMW champion Justin Thomas. Two-time BMW winner Dustin Johnson moved to world No. 1 and took over pole position in the FedExCup standings with an 11-shot victory at THE NORTHERN TRUST. Can he take another step towards his first FedExCup title at Olympia Fields?

snippet.title: Arsenal vs Liverpool | Key Moments | Community Shield 2020
snippet.description:
Heads Up FA Cup Final winners Arsenal beat Premier League champions Liverpool on penalties to win the Community Shield, after Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang and Takumi Minamino scored for their teams.

snippet.title: Sexual Harassment | Real Talk Season 2 Episode 4
snippet.description:
How would you know you‚Äôre being sexually harassed?

In this episode, the cast speak up about their unfortunate experience of being sexually harassed and give advice on what we should do if such a thing were to happen, not only to us, but to others as well.

If you have experienced any form of sexual harassment and are in need of help, please visit:

Sexual Assault Care Centre
http://sacc.aware.org.sg/

AWARE Singapore
https://www.aware.org.sg/

‚öî ‚öî When the Emperor of China issues a decree that one man per family must serve in the Imperial Army to defend the country from Northern invaders, Hua Mulan, the eldest daughter of an honored warrior, steps in to take the place of her ailing father. snippet.title: The Batman - DC FanDome Teaser
snippet.description:
Robert Pattinson is #TheBatman.

https://www.instagram.com/thebatman/
https://www.facebook.com/thebatman
https://twitter.com/thebatman
http://thebatman.com

From Warner Bros. Pictures comes ‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù with director Matt Reeves (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) at the helm and with Robert Pattinson (‚ÄúTenet,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lighthouse,‚Äù ‚ÄúGood Time‚Äù) starring as Gotham City‚Äôs vigilante detective, Batman, and billionaire Bruce Wayne.

Also in the star-studded ensemble as Gotham‚Äôs famous and infamous cast of characters are Zo√´ Kravitz (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald,‚Äù ‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù) as Selina Kyle; Paul Dano (‚ÄúLove & Mercy,‚Äù ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù) as Edward Nashton; Jeffrey Wright (the ‚ÄúHunger Games‚Äù films) as the GCPD‚Äôs James Gordon; John Turturro (the ‚ÄúTransformers‚Äù films) as Carmine Falcone; Peter Sarsgaard (‚ÄúThe Magnificent Seven,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlack Mass‚Äù) as Gotham D.A. Gil Colson; Barry Keoghan (‚ÄúDunkirk‚Äù) as Officer Stanley Merkel; Jayme Lawson (‚ÄúFarewell Amor‚Äù) as mayoral candidate Bella Re√°l; with Andy Serkis (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films, ‚ÄúBlack Panther‚Äù) as Alfred; and Colin Farrell (‚ÄúFantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them,‚Äù ‚ÄúDumbo‚Äù) as Oswald Cobblepot.

‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù was written by Matt Reeves & Peter Craig.  Reeves and Dylan Clark (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) are producing the film, with Simon Emanuel, Michael E. Uslan, Walter Hamada and Chantal Nong Vo serving as executive producers.  Reeves‚Äô behind-the-scenes creative team includes Oscar-nominated director of photography Greig Fraser (‚ÄúLion,‚Äù upcoming ‚ÄúDune‚Äù); his ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù production designer, James Chinlund; editors William Hoy (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) and Tyler Nelson (‚ÄúRememory‚Äù); Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book‚Äù); Oscar-nominated SFX supervisor Dominic Tuohy (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúStar Wars: Episode IX ‚Äì The Rise of Skywalker‚Äù); Oscar-nominated sound mixer Stuart Wilson (‚Äú1917,‚Äù the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise); Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù) and costume designers Glyn Dillon (the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise) and David Crossman (‚Äú1917,‚Äù the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise); hair designer Zoe Tahir (upcoming ‚ÄúNo Time to Die,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpectre‚Äù); and Oscar-nominated makeup designer Naomi Donne (‚Äú1917‚Äù).

Based on characters from DC.  Batman was created by Bob Kane with Bill Finger.  ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù is set to open in theaters October 1, 2021 in select 3D and 2D and IMAX theaters and will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

Uslan, Walter Hamada and Chantal Nong Vo serving as executive producers.  Reeves‚Äô behind-the-scenes creative team includes Oscar-nominated director of photography Greig Fraser (‚ÄúLion,‚Äù upcoming ‚ÄúDune‚Äù); his ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù production designer, James Chinlund; editors William Hoy (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) and Tyler Nelson (‚ÄúRememory‚Äù); Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book‚Äù); Oscar-nominated SFX supervisor Dominic Tuohy (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúStar Wars: Episode IX ‚Äì The Rise of Skywalker‚Äù); Oscar-nominated sound mixer Stuart Wilson (‚Äú1917,‚Äù the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise); Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù) and costume designers Glyn Dillon (the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise) and David Crossman (‚Äú1917,‚Äù the ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù franchise); hair designer Zoe Tahir (upcoming ‚ÄúNo Time to Die,‚Äù ‚ÄúSpectre‚Äù); and Oscar-nominated makeup designer Naomi Donne (‚Äú1917‚Äù).

Based on characters from DC.  Batman was created by Bob Kane with Bill Finger.  ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù is set to open in theaters October 1, 2021 in select 3D and 2D and IMAX theaters and will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Wonder Woman 1984 - Official Main Trailer
snippet.description:
The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman‚Äôs next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984‚Äù is Warner Bros. Pictures‚Äô follow up to the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first outing, 2017‚Äôs record-breaking ‚ÄúWonder Woman,‚Äù which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her ‚ÄúWonder Woman‚Äù team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (‚ÄúAm√©lie‚Äù), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (‚ÄúTopsy-Turvy‚Äù).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (‚ÄúUnited 93‚Äù) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (‚ÄúDunkirk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lion King‚Äù).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984.‚Äù  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

The new era of Wonder Woman begins here. #WW84 only in theaters.
 
http://www.facebook.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://twitter.com/WonderWomanFilm
http://www.instagram.com/wonderwomanfilm
http://wonderwoman1984.com
 
Fast forward to the 1980s as Wonder Woman‚Äôs next big screen adventure finds her facing two all-new foes: Max Lord and The Cheetah.  
 
With director Patty Jenkins back at the helm and Gal Gadot returning in the title role, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984‚Äù is Warner Bros. Pictures‚Äô follow up to the DC Super Hero‚Äôs first outing, 2017‚Äôs record-breaking ‚ÄúWonder Woman,‚Äù which took in $822 million at the worldwide box office.  The film also stars Chris Pine as Steve Trevor, Kristen Wiig as The Cheetah, Pedro Pascal as Max Lord, Robin Wright as Antiope, and Connie Nielsen as Hippolyta.
 
Charles Roven, Deborah Snyder, Zack Snyder, Patty Jenkins, Gal Gadot and Stephen Jones are producing the film.  Rebecca Steel Roven Oakley, Richard Suckle, Marianne Jenkins, Geoff Johns, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Wesley Coller are the executive producers.
 
Patty Jenkins directed from a screenplay she wrote with Geoff Johns & David Callaham, story by Jenkins & Johns, based on characters from DC.  Joining the director behind the scenes are several members of her ‚ÄúWonder Woman‚Äù team, including director of photography Matthew Jensen, Oscar-nominated production designer Aline Bonetto (‚ÄúAm√©lie‚Äù), and Oscar-winning costume designer Lindy Hemming (‚ÄúTopsy-Turvy‚Äù).  Oscar-nominated editor Richard Pearson (‚ÄúUnited 93‚Äù) is cutting the film.  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer (‚ÄúDunkirk,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lion King‚Äù).
 
Warner Bros. Pictures Presents an Atlas Entertainment/Stone Quarry Production, a Patty Jenkins Film, ‚ÄúWonder Woman 1984.‚Äù  Set to open in theaters in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX, it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
 
This film is rated PG-13 for sequences of action and violence.

#karikku #onam #malayalam

snippet.title: Dance Moms vs Extreme Acrobats - Insane Boys vs Girls Challenge | ft Abby Lee Miller
snippet.description:
Dance Moms Lilly and Ellie challenge two incredible gymnasts to an epic game of Boys vs Girls with Abby Lee Miller as the judge. 

THANK YOU FOR 5M!! ‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è‚ù§Ô∏è I‚Äôd like to thank each of you personally, so I‚Äôm doing a 24 hour open Zoom Sept 12&13 with surprise guests throughout! The Zoom will start at 11am EST on Sept 12, and I will share the link on my community page that morning. Make sure to subscribe and hit that bell so you'll get the post notification. 

TEXT ME: 917-540-3280

LIMITED BACK TO SCHOOL MERCH! ONE WEEK ONLY: https://shopjordanmatter.com

Many of my most popular videos feature Jack, Sol, Lilly, Ellie and Abby, but this is the first time they are all together in the same video!!! This is an epic Boys vs Girls photo challenge, and the loser has to recreate the winner's photos. We run around Santa Monica Beach all day, and I give each team the craziest challenges I can imagine. Wait until you see what I made them do- acrobatics, gymnastics, contortion, dance, flips and even a TikTok! At the end, Abby Lee Miller choreographs the final challenge and then picks the winner! snippet.title: New Zealand PM's PERFECT Response To Trump Attacks
snippet.description:
Trump attacked New Zealand, the Prime Minister's response was perfect. Ana Kasparian and Cenk Uygur discuss on The Young Turks. Keep Hope (and TYT) Alive: http://tyt.com/go

Read more here: https://www.npr.org/sections/coronavirus-live-updates/2020/08/18/903480195/trumps-claim-of-a-new-zealand-surge-is-patently-wrong-ardern-says

"New Zealand's Prime Minister Jacinda Ardern says President Trump's claim that New Zealand now has a "big surge" in coronavirus cases is "patently wrong," adding that the two countries are not comparable in how they handle the pandemic.

"We are still one of the best-performing countries in the world when it comes to COVID," Ardern said on Tuesday. "Our workers are focused on keeping it that way."

Trump's remarks came on Monday ‚Äî the same day New Zealand reported nine new cases, and the U.S. added nearly 42,000. But the U.S. president, speaking to supporters at an airport in Mankato, Minn., claimed New Zealand was an example of a country that had early success in fighting the outbreak, only to struggle now."*

snippet.title: SAOCOM 1B Mission
snippet.description:
SpaceX is targeting Sunday, August 30 at 7:18 p.m. EDT, or 23:18 UTC, for Falcon 9‚Äôs launch of the SAOCOM 1B mission, which will carry the SAOCOM 1B spacecraft to orbit in addition to two rideshare payloads, Tyvak-0172 and PlanetiQ‚Äôs GNOMES-1. The mission will lift off from Space Launch Complex 40 (SLC-40) at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station in Florida. A backup launch opportunity is available on Monday, August 31 at 7:19 p.m. EDT, or 23:19 UTC. This mission marks SpaceX‚Äôs first launch to a polar orbit from the East Coast, and the first polar launch from Florida in decades.

Falcon 9‚Äôs first stage previously launched Dragon to the International Space Station for SpaceX‚Äôs 19th and 20th commercial resupply missions, and it also supported launch of SpaceX‚Äôs ninth Starlink mission. Following stage separation, SpaceX will land Falcon 9 on Landing Zone 1 at Cape Canaveral Air Force Station. SAOCOM 1B will deploy approximately 14 minutes after launch, GNOMES-1 and Tyvak-0172 will deploy approximately 61 and 62 minutes after liftoff.

snippet.title: Losing Again: Trump's Postal Plot Backfires Amidst Bezos Feud | The Beat With Ari Melber | MSNBC
snippet.description:
Pres. Trump‚Äôs alleged efforts to subvert the Post Office for his own political agenda go beyond the current scandal over voting by mail. MSNBC‚Äôs Ari Melber reports on a long-running feud with billionaire Washington Post owner Jeff Bezos, including incriminating secret White House meetings reported by the Washington Post itself, and why the scandal matters now amidst allegations of election impropriety and the Postmaster General facing Congress, in a new installment of The Beat‚Äôs special Backstory series. (This interview is from MSNBC‚Äôs ‚ÄúThe Beat with Ari Melber, a news show covering politics, law and culture airing nightly at 6pm ET on MSNBC. http://www.thebeatwithari.com). Aired on 08/20/2020.

"Dance Moms" follows Abby Lee Miller and the nation's favorite tween dancers as they take on Hollywood while new auditions, new competitions, and new studios raise the stakes.

The road has not been easy for ‚ÄúDance Mom‚Äôs‚Äù star Abby Lee Miller. After completing her prison sentence last year, the famed dance instructor was diagnosed with non-Hodgkin‚Äôs lymphoma. But if anything, Abby has proven she is a fighter and is not ready to hang up the dance shoes. The new season of Dance Moms follows Abby as she rebuilds her dance company while battling the after-effects of cancer that has left her confined to a wheelchair. Abby is ready to get back to her life and do what she loves most‚Ä¶teaching students to dance! With the goal of putting her life, health and dance studio back together, Abby returns to where it all began ‚Äì the Abby Lee Dance Company in Pittsburgh.

snippet.title: Surviving the Hottest Place in the World
snippet.description:
Go to http://www.audible.com/yestheory or text yestheory to 500 500 to get one free audiobook, unlimited Audible originals and a 30-day free trial
New Seek Discomfort Summer Drop: https://www.seekdiscomfort.com/ live for only 72hrs!

This week after Death Valley hit the hottest temperature ever recorded... We decided to go and experience what 130F or 56C felt like... Both the best and worst idea we've ever had.

Does anyone read the description? I never really know to be honest. Well either way, this is Thomas and I'm a bit bored writing this so I'll just keep typing random things and see if anybody will notice. Conor was really upset that we kept him farting in the video so please ignore that part (or don't). Anyways, hope you liked the video we're actually pretty stoked with how it came out!

Check out Conor's channel here and tell him we sent you it'll make him very happy!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1E5Ti2P70zZxA4osS2MhiA

Thank you to Tommy, Tristan and Nathan for tagging along as our rescue team.

We have a 2nd channel! Make sure to subscribe to it here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTd7KzdwnFE3lm6LCfYDmUQ

If you want to join the Yes Fam Facebook group which is 100,000+ of our most engaged and badass community members, you can apply here: 
https://www.facebook.com/groups/yesfam/

Musicbed has amazing montage and cinematic music:

For an amazing b-roll and footage library, checkout: http://storyblocks.com/YesTheory

Who are we? 
We believe that life can be as fulfilling as you wish, so long as you're willing to seek discomfort. And we make videos about it.
